entry.title: Just landed: our brand new sushi collection
entry.summary:
We’re very excited to announce the launch of our brand new sushi collection with Yuki's Kitchen. From fresh sushi-grade wild fish to authentic Japanese ingredients – we now have everything you need to make handmade maki rolls in the comfort of your own kitchen.

entry.title: Say Hello to Our New Meat Range!
entry.summary:
As the summer approaches and the delicious smell of barbecues drift in the evening breeze, it’s the perfect time to share with you our exciting news... say hello to our whole new Meat range, including a brilliant Surf n Turf collection!

entry.title: Introducing Half Shell Gin
entry.summary:
We've created our very first Half Shell Gin – a unique spirit distilled with oyster shells, Amalfi lemon and kelp seaweed. It's distilled by the expert team at The Ginstitute, London.
